messages.text: Okay I’ve been typing and retyping this text message for like 2 hrs
and i’ve concluded there is no good way to start this conversation.
So, hi. I’m Dev’s friend Brian.
Hi Dev’s friend Brian. What’s up.
Haha, nothing besides being a nervous wreck lol.
No! Don’t be a nervous wreck. Haha Dev told me you were going to text me.
How do you guys know each other?
We met through my ex-girlfriend. Same major.
Oh, are you also pre-med?
OH GOD NO.
They’re both much smarter than me, lol.
I’m a comm major, I just had to take a science requirement.
Haha, yeah Dev is much smarter than me also.
Anytime we go to dinner with a group of friends he’s put in charge of dividing the bill.
So handy to have a genius around. He used to finish my labs for me.
So can I take you to dinner or something? I’ll bring a calculator.
That sounds nice :)
Friday at 7? I can pick you up.
yay can’t wait.
a few days later
Hey,  I know we had plans for dinner, but my roommate’s parents are in town...
I totally forgot I told her I’d go to dinner with her family.
Oh no.
I know, I suck :(
But I’m going to this party off campus tonight if you want to meet up a little later.
I’ll probably be there around 10-ish.
345 Gulch St., Apartment 3A
Oh, my ex used to live around there. Not too far.
Okay, let’s plan to meet there
Awesome! So sorry to do this to you
No, it’s not a problem.
Great! I can’t wait to see you.
a little bit later
Hey, I’m here at the party. You here yet?
Did you just get there?
Yeah, just got here
Like ten minutes ago. Don’t know anyone here…
Okay, sorry I’m running late, my roomie’s parents just kept pouring the wine haha
But my friend and I are en route right now.
Okay, see you soon.
a little bit later
Are you close?
Ok sorry this night keeps getting crazier
My friend who was gonna drive lost her wallet and went crazy
And now she doesn’t want to go out at all :(
Oh, I thought you said you were on your way
Yeah, we were just about to leave when she realized she didn’t have her wallet on her.
My roommate and I are just gonna walk to Kennelly’s Bar
You should join us!
Ugh ok
Or not, sorry if you’re like exhausted.
No no it’s all good, sorry, it’s just kind of a hike to get there from where I am
I know, i’m sorry for all of this
Was the party fun at least?
I bumped into an old high school classmate.
He now wears a cape everywhere, so that was weird.
Hahaha
Come meet us! I’d still love to see you.
Okay. Leaving now.
a little bit later
Random, but do you have any gum with you?
Gum?
Haha, IDK I need some gum. Would you hate me if I made you stop at CVS on the way?
For real?
Or you can let my breath smell like garlic for the rest of the night…
okay, I’ll make a pit stop.
a little bit later
Hey, are you still coming to Kennelly’s?
Yeah, on my way. There’s some traffic, but i’ll be there mad soon.
Okay, like where are you?
On the parkway.
Cause we might be going to a different bar soon, so maybe you should meet us there.
Wait, never mind.
Can I call you?
It’s really noisy in here.
Sorry, i think we are going to another bar actually.
I’ll tell you the name of it when I know.
Okay, please do…
a little bit later
K, so we are heading to The Black Dog, do you know where that is?
No.
I think it’s close
I don’t know the address, maybe you can Google it?
Are you there yet?
No, on the way though.
Come! We’ll probably get there at the same time.
I don’t know, I’m kind of close to my apartment and I think I might just call it a night.
No! 😕 sorry, I feel so bad for doing this to you.
I understand if you don’t want to come, but I promise I’ll make it worth it if you do ;)
Oh, it’s actually not that far. Ok, I’ll come by
Yay!
a little bit later
Hey, I’m at the black dog
You here yet?
Yeah, just got here
Standing right by the piano
I don’t see a piano…
It’s like to the side of the bar. I’m waving, do you see me?
There’s no piano here. I’m by the pool tables.
Pool tables?
Shit…
haha, wait i hope we’re at the same bar
Oh shit, it’s called the Bulldog, not the Black Dog, lol
Aye dios mio.
OMG sorry
Ugh, this is a disaster. We’re all kind of drunk and my friends are being idiots.
I was hoping you could come and bring the sanity :)
Hmm…
All right, I’ll drive over to the bulldog
Can’t wait!
a little bit later
My roommate is so drunk and kept insisting on going to the taco truck down the road...
so we’re on line to get tacos right now.
What? I just got to the bulldog
haha, sorry, we’re just a little ways down the block waiting for our tacos.
Okay, I’ll come over.
Hey, are you in the bar or are you coming to the taco truck?
a little bit later
You there?
okay, we’re going home now, sorry we didn’t get to meet up. Hope you get home safe.
the next day
Just want to make sure you’re still alive in case Dev asks, haha.
Definitely still alive.
I didn’t mean to disappear last night.
While I was looking for parking at the bulldog I ran into my ex-girlfriend, haha.
Oh. Hope that wasn’t awkward.
Umm…awkward isn’t the word.
Oh?
Well I have no plans tonight if you actually want to do that dinner like we planned originally.
I don’t think that’s gonna happen.
Oh no, are you busy?
No, but I have a girlfriend again.
